---
title: Chinese Beef & Veggie Stir-fry with Jasmine Rice
description: This beef stir-fry is infused with kecap manis and ginger, so it’s got a great savoury and zingy flavour. Ginger also helps tenderise the meat, as well as adding an unmistakeable pop. Of course, you can dial it back if zingy isn’t your thing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ba1d91cae08b57a884821c2-59f7249b.jpg
